name: Isabella Daniels
important: Looking for a roommate who is also tidy and respectful and that actually does their dishes.

name: Jenny Dayton
bio: Hey, I'm Jen, an outdoor adventurer exploring the boundless wilderness surrounding Denver. Beyond hiking and camping, I'm rock climbing in rugged canyons or whitewater rafting down rushing rivers. In the heart of Colorado's outdoor playground, my basecamp is a haven of adventure, where every expedition is an opportunity to connect with nature and push my limits.
important: Having in-unit washer and dryer is a must for me, as well as dishwasher and either a parking garage or in an area with street parking for my car.

name: Halle Harper
bio: Hi, I'm Halle, a history buff delving into Denver's rich heritage and storied past. When I'm not visiting museums or historic sites, I'm attending cultural events or exploring vintage neighborhoods. In the heart of the Mile High City, my home office is a portal to the past, where every artifact and archive tells a tale of Denver's fascinating history.
important: I have two cats that are partially out-door so a place with a backyard is ideal, also they are not dog friendly - so no one with dogs please!
